### CHANGE TRACKING NUMBER
PATCH http://app.xycargo.com/v1/shipments/1/tracking HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tracking_number": "SHPNEWTRACK12345"
}

### RESPONSE

{
  "status": "success",
  "code": 200,
  "shipment": {
    "shipment_id": 1,
    "tracking_number": "SHPNEWTRACK12345",
    "updated_at": "2025-10-20 15:00:00"
  },
  "message": "Tracking number changed successfully"
}

### UPDATE SHIPMENT STATUS
PATCH http://app.xycargo.com/v1/shipments/1/status HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "in_transit"
}

### RESPONSE

{
  "status": "success",
  "code": 200,
  "shipment": {
    "shipment_id": 1,
    "status": "in_transit",
    "updated_at": "2025-10-20 15:05:00"
  },
  "message": "Status updated successfully"
}

